        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Timeline Events",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0015.b022",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "If there are any symbols, events or other notes assigned to the current day, they must be resolved in the appropriate Campaign Round Step:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Acclimations: ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Acclimations upgrade your Exploration deck with new cards and are resolved in the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Exploration Step",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Battles:Timeline Battles",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " and additional Battles noted on the Timeline are resolved in the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Encounter Step",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Technology Breakthroughs:Structural Technolog",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "y  and ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Battle Technology",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " Breakthroughs are resolved in the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Advancement Step",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Advancements:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " All events added to the Timeline by using Argo Fa-cilities are resolved in the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Advancement Step",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Story Events: ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Any event leading directly to a story paragraph in the Storybook as well as any other events that are not Break-throughs, Advancements, Acclimations or Battles are Story Events and should be resolved in the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Story Step",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
